---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import haridusMin from '../assets/haridus_ja_teadusministeerium.png';
import RMIT from '../assets/RMIT.svg';
import telia from '../assets/telia.svg';
import rmk from '../assets/rmk.png';
import maksu_ja_tolliamet from '../assets/maksu_ja_tolliamet.svg';
import bigbank from '../assets/bigbank.svg';
import TEHIK from '../assets/TEHIK.svg';
import TWM from '../assets/TWM.png';
import andres from '../assets/andres.jpg'
import magnar from '../assets/magnar.jpg'
interface Props {
    lang: 'et' | 'en';
}

const { lang } = Astro.props;
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="container mt-36 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between gap-8 scroll-mt-24"
>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="mb-8 font-bold text-3xl text-center md:text-left">{lang === 'et' ? 'Mida oleme saavutanud' : 'What we have achieved'}</h3>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-12 text-justify">
        <p>
            {lang === 'et' ? 'Maand Solutions pakub digistrateegiat ja tarkvaralahendusi klientidele, kes seda kõige rohkem vajavad — alates riigiasutustest, kes läbivad keerulisi digitaalseid muutusi, kuni ettevõteteni, kes soovivad liikuda kiiremini kui nende praegune olukord võimaldab.' :
                'Maand Solutions delivers digital strategy and software solutions to the clients who need them most — from government institutions navigating complex digital transformations to companies looking to move faster than their current setup allows.'}
        </p>
        <p>
            {lang === 'et' ? 'Oleme väike meeskond ja see on meie tugevus, mitte nõrkus. Ei mingeid vahendajaid, ei mingeid ooteaegu, ei mingeid inimesi, kes su probleemi kolm nädalat hiljem sulle tagasi seletavad. Tood meile väljakutse — strateegilise, tehnilise või midagi vahepealset — ja me läheme tööle. Töö, mis tegelikult jõuab kohale.' :
                'We\'re a small team, and that\'s a feature not a bug. No hand-offs, no waiting rooms, no one explaining your problem back to you three weeks later. You bring us a challenge — strategic, technical, or somewhere in between — and we get to work. The kind of work that actually ships.'}</p>
        <p>
            {lang === 'et' ? 'Töötame erinevates valdkondades, alates avaliku sektori asutustest kuni erineva kasvuetapiga eraettevõteteni. Olenemata väljakutsest, on lähenemine alati sama: selge mõtlemine, puhas teostus ja tulemused, millele saab päriselt tugineda.' :
                'We work across sectors, from public institutions to private companies at various stages of growth. Whatever the challenge, the approach stays the same: clear thinking, clean execution, and zero tolerance for solutions that look good in a deck but fall apart in practice.'}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-8 items-center justify-items-center">
        <Image
            class="w-auto h-auto"
            src={haridusMin}
            alt="Haridus- ja Teadusministeerium"
        />
        <Image
            src={RMIT}
            alt="RMIT"
        />
        <Image
            src={telia}
            alt="Telia"
        />
        <Image
            src={rmk}
            alt="RMK"
        />
        <Image
            src={maksu_ja_tolliamet}
            alt="Maksu- ja Tolliamet"
        />
        <Image
            src={bigbank}
            alt="Bigbank"
        />
        <Image
            src={TEHIK}
            alt="TEHIK"
        />
        <Image
            src={TWM}
            alt="twm"
        />
    </div>
  </div>
    <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <li class="border border-black p-4 list-none rounded-2xl min-h-40">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">37</h2>
            <p>{lang === 'et' ? 'Edukat projekti' : 'Completed projects'}</p>
        </li>

        <li class="bg-black text-white p-4 list-none rounded-2xl min-h-40">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">5</h2>
            <p>{lang === 'et' ? 'Töötajat' : 'Employees'}</p>
        </li>

        <li class="bg-sand p-4 list-none rounded-2xl min-h-40">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">3 000 000</h2>
            <p>{lang === 'et' ? 'Käive' : 'Revenue'}</p>
        </li>

        <li class="bg-primary p-4 list-none rounded-2xl min-h-40">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">37</h2>
            <p>{lang === 'et' ? 'Rahulolevat klienti' : 'Satisfied clients'}</p>
        </li>
    </div>
</section>

<section
        id="team"
        class="container mx-auto mt-24 scroll-mt-24 px-4"
>
    <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl text-center">
        {lang === 'et' ? 'Meie meeskond' : 'Our team'}
    </h3>

    <div class="mt-12 text-black">

        <!-- First row (2 people) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <Image src={magnar} alt="Magnar Aruoja" class="w-40 h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full object-cover" />
                <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-center">Magnar Aruoja</p>
                <p class="font-medium text-center">{lang === 'et' ? 'Roll' : 'Role'}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <Image src={andres} alt="Andres Saaremõts" class="w-40 h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full object-cover" />
                <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-center">Andres Saaremõts</p>
                <p class="font-medium text-center">{lang === 'et' ? 'Roll' : 'Role'}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Second row (3 people) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <Image src={andres} alt="Carolina Kask" class="w-40 h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full object-cover" />
                <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-center">Carolina Kask</p>
                <p class="font-medium text-center">{lang === 'et' ? 'Roll' : 'Role'}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <Image src={andres} alt="Timo Kaasik" class="w-40 h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full object-cover" />
                <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-center">Timo Kaasik</p>
                <p class="font-medium text-center">{lang === 'et' ? 'Noorem Tarkvaraarendaja' : 'Junior Software Developer'}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <Image src={andres} alt="Aksel Kaasik" class="w-40 h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 rounded-full object-cover" />
                <p class="mt-2 font-medium text-center">Aksel Kaasik</p>
                <p class="font-medium text-center">{lang === 'et' ? 'Noorem Tarkvaraarendaja' : 'Junior Software Developer'}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>